thread.title_full: American Frame americanframe.com reviewed by James

author: James
title: James
text: This was my first order from American Frame, and I was delighted. Everything was packaged well to avoid any damage, Backing board, matting and frame components were perfectly cut and sized for my photo as ordered on the web site. Everything was in perfect condition. After having looked at numerous web sites that offered components for mounting my photographs, I selected American Frame based on their intuitive web site, and the quality of their materials. I was not disappointed, and highly recommend their products and services.
